<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>The Rest Year — Postpartum Doula Care with Yuli Smith, LM·CPM·IBCLC</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,300;0,9..144,400;0,9..144,500;1,9..144,300;1,9..144,400&family=Inter+Tight:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --cream: #f5efe6;
    --cream-deep: #ede4d4;
    --ink: #2a2520;
    --ink-soft: #5c544a;
    --clay: #9c4a2e;
    --clay-deep: #7a3621;
    --gold: #d9a574;
    --line: rgba(42, 37, 32, 0.14);
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  html, body { height: 100%; }

  body {
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: 'Inter Tight', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.6;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
    opacity: 0.35;
    mix-blend-mode: multiply;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 200 200' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.85' numOctaves='2' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3CfeColorMatrix values='0 0 0 0 0.16 0 0 0 0 0.14 0 0 0 0 0.12 0 0 0 0.18 0'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
  }

  body::after {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    top: -20%;
    right: -10%;
    width: 60vw;
    height: 60vw;
    max-width: 800px;
    max-height: 800px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(217, 165, 116, 0.35) 0%, rgba(217, 165, 116, 0) 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .display {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 144;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.02;
  }

  .top-strip {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
    padding: 28px 56px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .brand {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 18px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .brand em {
    color: var(--clay);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .top-meta {
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }

  main {
    flex: 1;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    padding: 56px 56px 40px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.25fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .lead { position: relative; }

  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--clay);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .eyebrow::before {
    content: '';
    width: 32px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--clay);
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(44px, 6.2vw, 84px);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--clay);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .lede {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    max-width: 540px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .bio-mini {
    border-left: 2px solid var(--clay);
    padding: 4px 0 4px 20px;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  .bio-mini p {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .bio-mini strong {
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .cta-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    padding: 17px 34px;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--cream);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--clay-deep);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .btn-ghost {
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink);
    padding: 4px 2px;
    transition: color 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
  }

  .btn-ghost:hover { color: var(--clay); border-color: var(--clay); }

  .care-line {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px 16px;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .care-line .dot {
    width: 4px;
    height: 4px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--clay);
  }

  .care-line span:not(.dot) { white-space: nowrap; }

  .portrait-wrap { position: relative; }

  .portrait {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 4/5;
    max-width: 460px;
    margin-left: auto;
    background: var(--cream-deep);
    border-radius: 2px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 40px 80px -40px rgba(42, 37, 32, 0.45),
                0 0 0 1px rgba(42, 37, 32, 0.06);
  }

  .portrait img {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 30%;
    filter: saturate(0.95) contrast(1.02);
  }

  /* Subtle warm gradient overlay to tie photo into the cream/clay palette */
  .portrait::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg,
      rgba(245, 239, 230, 0) 0%,
      rgba(245, 239, 230, 0) 55%,
      rgba(42, 37, 32, 0.25) 100%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .credentials-tag {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 20px;
    left: 20px;
    right: 20px;
    background: rgba(245, 239, 230, 0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    padding: 16px 20px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    border-radius: 2px;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .credentials-tag .name {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .credentials-tag .creds {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--clay);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .quote-mark {
    position: absolute;
    top: -30px;
    right: 20px;
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: 200px;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--clay);
    opacity: 0.12;
    font-style: italic;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .bottom-strip {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
    padding: 22px 56px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    background: var(--cream-deep);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }

  .bottom-strip strong {
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .bottom-strip a { color: var(--ink-soft); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.3s; }
  .bottom-strip a:hover { color: var(--clay); }

  .fade-up { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); animation: fadeUp 0.85s ease forwards; }
  .fade-up.d1 { animation-delay: 0.05s; }
  .fade-up.d2 { animation-delay: 0.18s; }
  .fade-up.d3 { animation-delay: 0.32s; }
  .fade-up.d4 { animation-delay: 0.46s; }
  .fade-up.d5 { animation-delay: 0.6s; }
  .fade-up.d6 { animation-delay: 0.74s; }

  @keyframes fadeUp { to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    main { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 56px; padding: 40px 32px; }
    .portrait { max-width: 380px; margin: 0 auto; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .top-strip, .bottom-strip { padding: 18px 24px; }
    .top-meta { display: none; }
    main { padding: 32px 24px; }
    .bio-mini { padding-left: 16px; }
    .bio-mini p { font-size: 15px; }
    .lede { font-size: 16px; }
    .care-line { font-size: 11px; }
    .bottom-strip { flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; text-align: center; font-size: 11px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="top-strip">
  <div class="brand">The Rest <em>Year</em></div>
  <div class="top-meta">
    Postpartum Doula Care &nbsp;·&nbsp; Temecula &amp; Inland Empire
  </div>
</header>

<main>
  <div class="lead">
    <div class="eyebrow fade-up d1">Now booking · 2026</div>
    <h1 class="display fade-up d2">The first year<br>deserves a <em>guide.</em></h1>
    <p class="lede fade-up d3">
      Skilled, in-home postpartum support from a Licensed Midwife and IBCLC who's been doing this work since 2015. Meals made. Feedings figured out. You, finally able to rest.
    </p>

    <div class="bio-mini fade-up d4">
      <p>
        I'm <strong>Yuli</strong> — postpartum doula since 2015, credentialed as <strong>LM, CPM, and IBCLC</strong> in 2022. After years in the homebirth and lactation world, I'm returning to where I started: walking into your home, taking the load off, and making sure the fourth trimester is something you actually get to experience — not just survive.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-row fade-up d5">
      <a href="mailto:hello@therestyear.com?subject=Postpartum%20Doula%20Inquiry" class="btn-primary">Book a Consult →</a>
      <a href="https://iemidwifery.com" class="btn-ghost">Also a midwife</a>
    </div>

    <div class="care-line fade-up d6">
      <span>Daytime &amp; Overnight Support</span>
      <span class="dot"></span>
      <span>Lactation (IBCLC)</span>
      <span class="dot"></span>
      <span>Belly Binding &amp; Recovery</span>
      <span class="dot"></span>
      <span>Sibling &amp; Family Care</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="portrait-wrap fade-up d3">
    <span class="quote-mark">"</span>
    <div class="portrait">
      <img src="yuli-portrait.jpg" alt="Yuli Smith, postpartum doula, sitting in a desert landscape">
      <div class="credentials-tag">
        <div class="name">Yuli Smith</div>
        <div class="creds">LM · CPM · IBCLC</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>

<footer class="bottom-strip">
  <div><strong>Inquire:</strong> &nbsp; <a href="mailto:hello@therestyear.com">hello@therestyear.com</a></div>
  <div>© 2026 The Rest Year &nbsp;·&nbsp; Temecula, CA</div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
